 medium heat. Fry balls in batches for 5 minutes until golden brown, turning occasionally, adding up to 2 Tbsp extra oil as necessary. Serve warm or cold (see tip)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["These bean balls are so versatile; serve with salad and your favourite dressing, with a ragu sauce with rice or eat them as a snack on the go!<br>"],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 10m","30 pieces"]}